{"tid":1346890,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"無論727定728元朗，大家在這一星期請盡量抽撥時間做至少30分鐘的運動","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T13:44:25.000Z","uid":38861,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2ca465078761d45509c5a2f66153115d6e0bfd","tid":1346890,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:00:49.000Z","msg":"現在黑警合作出哂面，警署落閘，999cut線，警方再也無能保護市民，必要時候大家就要靠自己。<br />\n<br />\n雖然距離727或728不足一星期，但有心鍛煉身體絕不怕遲，體力在短期及長遠來說也是非常重要的。<br />\n<br />\n無論你工時長與否，作為一個有承擔的香港人，請嘗試在這星期建立一個短期目標，至少在下列三項裡做一項：<br />\n<br />\n1）每日/隔日堅持跑步20-30分鐘<br />\n<br />\n2）每日做1-2分鐘plank<br />\n<br />\n3）罷食垃圾食物（KFC/麥當勞）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你把持唔住的時候，請你諗番昨晚那幫元朗黑社會是如何的猖狂，化悲憤轉為動力，好好鍛煉身體及保持身體健康，為727或728也好，為長遠健康也好，好使能抵擋任何日常的不公義。"},{"pid":"c40742c4c1be3898481201e32c2bc6a4d263ba72","tid":1346890,"uid":216421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"要鍛鍊好自己嘅身體抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723dc042d88098b2c51c076e9c8e383f59ed3d72","tid":1346890,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c40742c4c1be3898481201e32c2bc6a4d263ba72","tid":1346890,"uid":216421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"要鍛鍊好自己嘅身體抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"再也不要俾任何藉口自己！"},{"pid":"33f50cc269b371c3b2292368f7238a4224d2e7e9","tid":1346890,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"老實講班友冇train過 你夠佢狠 兩個打佢一個一定冇問題"},{"pi